1:1 Pawulo wahamagariwe kuba intumwa ya Yesu Kristo nk'uko Imana yashatse, na Sositeni mwene Data, 
1:2   
1:3 Ubuntu n'amahoro bibe muri mwe, biva ku Mana Data wa twese no ku Mwami Yesu Kristo.
1:4 Mbashimira Imana yanjye iteka nishimira ubuntu bwayo mwaherewe muri Kristo Yesu, 
1:5 kuko muri byose mwatungiwe muri we, mu byo muvuga byose no mu bwenge bwose, 
1:6 kuko ubuhamya twahamije Kristo bwakomejwe muri mwe, 
1:7 bituma mutagira impano yose mubura, mutegereza guhishurwa k'Umwami wacu Yesu Kristo. 
1:8 Ni we uzabakomeza kugeza ku mperuka, kugira ngo mutazabaho umugayo ku munsi w'Umwami wacu Yesu Kristo. 
1:9 Imana ni iyo kwizerwa, yabahamagariye gufatanya n'Umwana wayo Yesu Kristo Umwami wacu.
1:10 Ariko bene Data, ndabingingira mu izina ry'Umwami wacu Yesu Kristo kugira ngo mwese muvuge kumwe, kandi he kugira ibice biremwa muri mwe, ahubwo muhurize hamwe rwose muhuje imitima n'inama, 
1:11 kuko bene Data nabwiwe ibyanyu n'abo kwa Kilowe, yuko habonetse intonganya muri mwe. 
1:12  Icyo mvuze ngiki, ni uko umuntu wese muri mwe avuga ati “Jyeweho ndi uwa Pawulo”, undi akavuga ati “Ariko jyeweho ndi uwa Apolo”, undi na we ati “Jyeweho ndi uwa Kefa”, undi ati “Jyeweho ndi uwa Kristo.” 
1:13 Mbese Kristo yagabanijwemo ibice? Pawulo ni we wababambiwe? Cyangwa mwabatijwe mu izina rya Pawulo?
1:14   </span><span class="note x"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body">    Ibyak 18.8; 19.29; Rom 16.23  
1:15 kugira ngo hatagira umuntu uvuga yuko mwabatijwe mu izina ryanjye. 
1:16  Icyakora nabatije n'abo kwa Sitefana, uretse abo sinzi yuko hari undi nabatije 
1:17 kuko Kristo atantumye kubatiza, ahubwo yantumye kubwiriza ubutumwa bwiza ariko ntavugisha ubwenge bw'amagambo, kugira ngo umusaraba wa Kristo udahinduka ubusa.
1:18 Ijambo ry'umusaraba ku barimbuka ni ubupfu, ariko kuri twebwe abakizwa ni imbaraga z'Imana, 
1:19   
1:20   </span><span class="note x"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body">    Yobu 12.17; Yes 19.12; 33.18; 44.25  
1:21 Kuko ubwo ubwenge bw'Imana bwategetse ko ab'isi badaheshwa kumenya Imana n'ubwenge bw'isi, Imana yishimiye gukirisha abayizera ubupfu bw'ibibwirizwa. 
1:22 Dore Abayuda basaba ibimenyetso naho Abagiriki bo bashakashaka ubwenge, 
1:23 ariko twebweho tubabwiriza ibya Kristo wabambwe. Uwo ku Bayuda ni ikigusha, ku banyamahanga ni ubupfu, 
1:24 ariko ku bahamagawe b'Abayuda n'Abagiriki ni Kristo, ari we mbaraga z'Imana kandi ni ubwenge bwayo, 
1:25 kuko ubupfu bw'Imana burusha abantu ubwenge, kandi intege nke z'Imana zirusha abantu imbaraga.
1:26 Muzirikane guhamagarwa kwanyu bene Data, yuko ab'ubwenge bw'abantu bahamagawe atari benshi, n'abakomeye bahamagawe atari benshi, n'imfura zahamagawe atari nyinshi. 
1:27 Ahubwo Imana yatoranije abaswa bo mu isi ngo ikoze isoni abanyabwenge, kandi yatoranije ibinyantege nke byo mu isi ngo ikoze isoni ibikomeye, 
1:28 kandi n'ibyoroheje byo mu isi n'ibihinyurwa n'ibitariho, Imana yarabitoranije ngo ihindure ubusa ibiriho, 
1:29 kugira ngo hatagira umuntu wīrāta imbere y'Imana. 
1:30 Ni yo ibaha kuba muri Kristo Yesu waduhindukiye ubwenge buva ku Mana, no gukiranuka no kwezwa no gucungurwa, 
1:31  kugira ngo bibe nk'uko byanditswe ngo “Uwīrāta yīrāte Uwiteka.”
2:1 Ni cyo gituma bene Data, ubwo nazaga iwanyu ntaje ndi umuhanga n'intyoza yo kuvuga, cyangwa mfite ubwenge buhebuje mbabwira ibihamya by'Imana, 
2:2 kuko nagambiriye kutagira ikindi mbamenyesha</span><span class="note f"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body"><span class="fk">mbamenyesha: </span><span class="ft"> cyangwa, menya muri mwe.
2:3  Nabanaga namwe mfite intege nke, ntinya mpinda umushyitsi mwinshi, 
2:4 n'ibyo navugaga nkabwiriza ntibyari amagambo y'ubwenge yo kwemeza abantu, ahubwo byari ibigaragaza Umwuka n'imbaraga, 
2:5 kugira ngo kwizera kwanyu kudahagararira ku bwenge bw'abantu, ahubwo mu mbaraga z'Imana.
2:6 Icyakora ubwenge tubuvuga mu batunganijwe rwose, ariko ubwo bwenge si ubw'iki gihe cyangwa ubw'abatware b'iki gihe bashiraho. 
2:7 Ahubwo tuvuga ubwenge bw'ubwiru bw'Imana ari bwo bwenge bwahishwe, Imana yaringanije ibihe byose bitarabaho ngo buduheshe icyubahiro. 
2:8 Mu batware b'iki gihe nta wabumenye, kuko iyo babumenya ntibaba barabambye Umwami w'icyubahiro. 
2:9   
2:10 Ariko Imana yabiduhishurishije Umwuka wayo, kuko Umwuka arondora byose ndetse n'amayoberane y'Imana. 
2:11 Mbese ni nde mu bantu wamenya ibyo undi atekereza, keretse umwuka wa wa wundi umurimo? N'iby'Imana ni ko biri, nta wabimenya keretse Umwuka wayo.
2:12 Ariko twebweho ntitwahawe ku mwuka w'iyi si, ahubwo twahawe uwo Mwuka uva ku Mana kugira ngo tumenye ibyo Imana yaduhereye ubuntu, 
2:13 ari byo tuvuga ariko ntitubivugisha amagambo akomoka mu bwenge bw'abantu, ahubwo tubivugisha akomoka ku Mwuka, dusobanuza iby'Umwuka iby'umwuka bindi.</span><span class="note f"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body"><span class="fk">dusobanuza . . . bindi: </span><span class="ft"> cyangwa, tugereranya iby'Umwuka n'iby'umwuka bindi.
2:14 Ariko umuntu wa kamere ntiyemera iby'Umwuka w'Imana kuko ari ubupfu kuri we, akaba atabasha kubimenya kuko bisobanurwa mu buryo bw'Umwuka. 
2:15 Ariko umuntu w'Umwuka arondora byose, nyamara ubwe nta wumurondora. 
2:16  Mbese ni nde wigeze kumenya icyo Uwiteka atekereza ngo amwigishe? Nyamara twebwe dufite gutekereza kwa Kristo.
3:1 Bene Data, sinabashije kuvugana namwe nk'uvugana n'ab'Umwuka, ahubwo navuganye namwe nk'uvugana n'aba kamere, cyangwa abana b'impinja bo muri Kristo. 
3:2  Nabaramije amata, sinabagaburiye ibyokurya bikomeye, kuko mwari mutarabibasha. Kandi na none ntimurabibasha 
3:3 kuko mukiri aba kamere. Ubwo muri mwe harimo ishyari n'amahane, mbese ntimubaye aba kamere koko ntimugenza nk'abantu? 
3:4   
3:5 Mbese ye, Apolo ni iki? Kandi Pawulo ni iki? Si abagaragu batumye mwizera nk'uko Imana yabahaye umurimo? 
3:6  Ni jye wateye imbuto Apolo na we arazuhira, ariko Imana ni yo yazikujije. 
3:7 Nuko utera nta cyo aba ari cyo cyangwa uwuhīra, keretse Imana ikuza. 
3:8 Utera n'uwuhīra barahwanye kandi umuntu wese azahembwa nk'uko yakoze umurimo we, 
3:9 kuko twembi Imana ari yo dukorera namwe mukaba umurima w'Imana n'inzu yayo.
3:10 Nk'uko ubuntu bw'Imana nahawe bungana, nashyizeho urufatiro nk'umwubakisha mukuru w'ubwenge, undi yubakaho. Ariko umuntu wese yirinde uko yubakaho, 
3:11 kuko nta rundi rufatiro umuntu abasha gushyiraho keretse urwashyizweho, ari rwo Yesu Kristo. 
3:12 Ariko umuntu niyubaka kuri urwo rufatiro izahabu cyangwa ifeza, cyangwa amabuye y'igiciro cyinshi cyangwa ibiti, cyangwa ibyatsi cyangwa ibikenyeri, 
3:13 umurimo w'umuntu wese uzerekanwa. Urya munsi ni wo uzawerekana kuko uzahishuzwa umuriro, akaba ari wo kandi uzagerageza umurimo w'umuntu wese. 
3:14 Umurimo w'umuntu, uwo yubatse kuri urwo rufatiro nugumaho azahabwa ingororano, 
3:15 ariko umurimo w'umuntu nushya azabura inyungu,</span><span class="note f"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body"><span class="fk">azabura inyungu: </span><span class="ft"> cyangwa, azahomba.
3:16   </span><span class="note x"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body">    1 Kor 6.19; 2 Kor 6.16  
3:17 Umuntu utsemba urusengero rw'Imana, Imana izamutsemba kuko urusengero rw'Imana ari urwera, kandi urwo rusengero ni mwe.
3:18 Ntihakagire umuntu wishuka: umuntu wese wo muri mwe niyibwira ko ari umunyabwenge ku by'iki gihe, abe umuswa kugira ngo abone uko aba umunyabwenge nyakuri. 
3:19  Mbese ntimuzi ko ubwenge bw'iyi si ari ubupfu ku Mana? Kuko byanditswe ngo “Itegesha abanyabwenge uburiganya bwabo.” 
3:20  Kandi ngo “Uwiteka azi ibyo abanyabwenge batekereza ko bitagira umumaro.” 
3:21 Nuko ntihakagire umuntu wīrāta abantu, 
3:22 kuko byose ari ibyanyu naho yaba Pawulo cyangwa Apolo cyangwa Kefa, cyangwa isi cyangwa ubugingo cyangwa urupfu, cyangwa ibiriho cyangwa ibizaba. Byose ni ibyanyu 
3:23 namwe muri aba Kristo, Kristo na we ni uw'Imana.
4:1 Nuko rero abantu bajye badutekereza yuko turi abakozi ba Kristo, n'ibisonga byeguriwe ubwiru bw'Imana. 
4:2 Kandi ibisonga bishakwaho ko biba abanyamurava. 
4:3 Ni cyo gituma kuri jye bitagira icyo bintwara rwose gucirwa urubanza namwe cyangwa n'abanyarukiko b'abantu, kuko ndetse nanjye ubwanjye nticira urubanza 
4:4 kuko ari nta cyo niyiziho. Nyamara si icyo kintsindishiriza, ahubwo Umwami ni we uncira urubanza. 
4:5 Ni cyo gituma mudakwiriye guca urubanza rw'ikintu cyose igihe cyarwo kitarasohora, kugeza ubwo Umwami wacu azaza agatangaza ibyari byahishwe mu mwijima, kandi akagaragaza n'imigambi yo mu mitima. Ubwo ni bwo umuntu wese azahabwa n'Imana ishimwe rimukwiriye.
4:6 Nuko bene Data, ibyo mbyigereranijeho jyewe na Apolo ku bwanyu nk'ubacira umugani, kugira ngo ibyo mvuze kuri twe bibigishe kudatekereza ibirenze ibyanditswe, hatagira umuntu wihimbaza arwana ishyaka ry'umwe agahinyura undi. 
4:7 Mbese ni nde wabatandukanije n'abandi? Kandi icyo mufite mutahawe ni igiki? Ariko niba mwaragihawe ni iki gituma mwīrāta nk'abatagihawe?
4:8 Mumaze guhaga, mumaze gutunga ndetse mwimye nk'abami tutari kumwe. Yemwe icyampa mukima</span><span class="note f"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body"><span class="fk">yemwe . . . mukima: </span><span class="ft"> cyangwa, kandi burya mbifuriza kwima.
4:9 Nibwira yuko twebwe intumwa Imana yatwerekanye hanyuma y'abandi nk'abaciriwe urubanza rwo gupfa, kuko twahindutse ibishungero by'ab'isi n'iby'abamarayika n'abantu. 
4:10 Twebweho turi abapfu ku bwa Kristo, naho mwebweho muri abanyabwenge muri Kristo: turi abanyantege nke, ariko mwe muri ab'imbaraga, muri ab'icyubahiro naho twe turi ab'igisuzuguriro. 
4:11 Kugeza na n'ubu twishwe n'inzara n'inyota kandi twambaye ubusa, dukubitwa ibipfunsi, turi inzererezi, 
4:12  dukoresha amaboko yacu imirimo y'imiruho. Iyo badututse tubasabira umugisha, iyo turenganijwe turihangana, 
4:13 iyo dushebejwe turinginga. Kugeza ubu twagizwe nk'umwavu w'isi n'ibiharurwa by'ibintu byose.
4:14 Ibyo simbyandikiye kubakoza isoni, ahubwo mbyandikiye kubahugura nk'abana banjye nkunda, 
4:15 kuko nubwo mufite muri Kristo ababayobora inzovu, ntimufite ba so benshi. Ni jye wababyaje ubutumwa bwiza muri Kristo Yesu. 
4:16  Nuko rero ndabinginga kugira ngo munyigane. 
4:17 Ni cyo gitumye mbatumaho Timoteyo, umwana wanjye nkunda ukiranukira Umwami wacu. Azabibutsa inzira zanjye zo muri Kristo, nk'uko nigisha hose mu matorero yose.
4:18 Ariko bamwe barihimbaza bibwira yuko ntazaza iwanyu. 
4:19 Nyamara nzaza vuba Umwami nabishaka, kandi sinzamenya amagambo y'abo bishyashyarika gusa, ahubwo nzamenya imbaraga zabo 
4:20 kuko ubwami bw'Imana atari ubw'amagambo, ahubwo ari ubw'imbaraga. 
4:21 Mbese murashaka iki? Ko nza iwanyu nzanye inkoni, cyangwa ko nzana urukundo n'umutima w'ubugwaneza?
5:1   </span><span class="note x"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body">    Guteg 22.30  
5:2 Namwe murihimbaza aho kubabara, kandi ari byo byari bibakwiriye ngo uwakoze icyo cyaha akurwe muri mwe, 
5:3 kuko jyewe nubwo ntari kumwe namwe mu mubiri nahoranye namwe mu mwuka, kandi ubwo bimeze bityo namaze gucira ho iteka uwakoze ibisa bityo nk'aho mpari, 
5:4 kandi ubwo nari nteraniye hamwe namwe mu mutima wanjye dufite ububasha bw'Umwami wacu Yesu, nahawe ubutware na we 
5:5 kugira ngo uwo muntu muhe Satani umubiri we urimbuke, umwuka we ubone kuzakira ku munsi w'Umwami Yesu.
5:6   </span><span class="note x"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body">    Gal 5.9  
5:7  Nuko nimwiyezeho umusemburo wa kera kugira ngo mube irobe rishya, mube mutakirimo umusemburo wa kera koko kuko Pasika yacu yatambwe, ari we Kristo. 
5:8   
5:9 Nabandikiye muri rwa rwandiko ko mutifatanya n'abasambanyi. 
5:10 Ariko sinavuze yuko mudaterana rwose n'abasambanyi bo mu b'iy'isi, cyangwa abifuza ibibi cyangwa abanyazi cyangwa abasenga ibishushanyo, kuko iyo biba bityo mwari mukwiriye kuva mu isi. 
5:11 Ahubwo none nabandikiye ko mutifatanya n'uwitwa mwene Data, niba ari umusambanyi cyangwa uwifuza ibibi, cyangwa usenga ibishushanyo cyangwa utukana, cyangwa umusinzi cyangwa umunyazi, umeze atyo ntimugasangire na we.
5:12 Mbese mpuriye he no gucira abo hanze urubanza? Namwe abo mucira urubanza si abo muri mwe? 
5:13  Ariko abo hanze Imana ni yo izabacira ho iteka. Mukure uwo munyabyaha muri mwe.
6:1 Iyo umuntu wo muri mwe afite icyo apfa na mugenzi we, mbese ahangāra kuburanira ku bakiranirwa ntaburanire ku bera? 
6:2 Ntimuzi yuko abera bazacira ab'isi urubanza? Kandi ubwo ari mwe muzacira ab'isi urubanza, ntimushobora no guca imanza z'ibintu bito hanyuma y'ibindi? 
6:3 Ntimuzi ndetse yuko tuzacira abamarayika urubanza, nkanswe iby'ubu bugingo? 
6:4 Nuko rero niba mufite imanza zo gucibwa zerekeye ku by'ubu bugingo, ni iki gituma mubishyiraho abatagira icyo bahuriyeho n'Itorero ngo abe ari bo bazica? Ibyo mbivugiye kubakoza isoni. 
6:5 Mbese koko nta munyabwenge n'umwe uba muri mwe, wabasha gucira bene Se urubanza? 
6:6 Ahubwo mwene Data akaburana na mwene Data wundi, kandi baburanira ku batizera?
6:7 Nuko mumaze kubonekaho icyaha rwose, kuko muburana musubiranamo. Mbese ni iki gituma mudahitamo ahubwo kugirirwa nabi? Ni iki gituma mudahitamo guhuguzwa? 
6:8 Ariko ni mwe ubwanyu mugirirana nabi muhuguzanya, kandi abo mugirira mutyo ni bene Data. 
6:9 Ntimuzi yuko abakiranirwa batazaragwa ubwami bw'Imana? Ntimwishuke. Abahehesi cyangwa abasenga ibishushanyo cyangwa abasambanyi, cyangwa ibitingwa cyangwa abagabo bendana, 
6:10 cyangwa abajura cyangwa abifuza, cyangwa abasinzi cyangwa abatukana cyangwa abanyazi, bene abo ntibazaragwa ubwami bw'Imana. 
6:11 Kandi bamwe muri mwe mwari nka bo ariko mwaruhagiwe mwarejejwe, mwatsindishirijwe n'Umwuka w'Imana yacu mu izina ry'Umwami Yesu Kristo.
6:12   </span><span class="note x"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body">    1 Kor 10.23  
6:13 Ibyokurya ni iby'inda, n'inda na yo ni iy'ibyokurya, nyamara Imana izabitsemba byombi. Nuko rero umubiri si uwo gusambana ahubwo ni uw'Umwami, kandi Umwami na we ni uw'umubiri. 
6:14 Kandi ubwo Imana yazuye Umwami Yesu, natwe izatuzurisha imbaraga zayo.
6:15 Ntimuzi yuko imibiri yanyu ari ingingo za Kristo? Mbese noneho ntore ingingo za Kristo, nkazihindura ingingo za maraya? Ntibikabeho! 
6:16  Ntimuzi yuko uwifatanya na maraya aba abaye umubiri umwe na we? Kuko Imana yavuze iti “Bombi bazaba umubiri umwe.” 
6:17 Ariko uwifatanya n'Umwami Yesu aba abaye umwuka umwe na we.
6:18 Muzibukīre gusambana. Ibindi byaha byose umuntu akora bikorerwa inyuma y'umubiri, ariko usambana aba akoze icyaha cyo mu mubiri we. 
6:19  Mbese ntimuzi yuko imibiri yanyu ari insengero z'Umwuka Wera uri muri mwe, uwo mufite wavuye ku Mana? Kandi ntimuri abanyu ngo mwigenge 
6:20 kuko mwaguzwe igiciro. Nuko rero mutume imibiri yanyu ihimbaza Imana.
7:1 Ibyerekeye ibyo mwanyandikiye, ibyiza ni uko umugabo adakora ku mugore. 
7:2 Ariko ku bwo kwirinda gusambana, umugabo wese agire uwe mugore, n'umugore wese agire uwe mugabo. 
7:3 Umugabo ahe umugore we ibimukwiriye kandi n'umugore na we abigenze atyo ku mugabo we, 
7:4 kuko umugore adatwara umubiri we ahubwo utwarwa n'umugabo we, kandi n'umugabo na we adatwara umubiri we ahubwo utwarwa n'umugore we. 
7:5 Ntimukimane keretse ahari musezeranye igihe, kugira ngo mubone uburyo bwo gusenga, kandi mwongere guhura Satani atabagerageresha iruba ry'imibiri yanyu.
7:6 Ariko ibyo mbivuze ku bwanjye si amategeko mbategeka, 
7:7 kuko nashaka ko abantu bose bamera nkanjye, ariko umuntu wese afite impano ye yahawe n'Imana, umwe ukwe undi ukwe.
7:8 Abatararongorana kandi n'abapfakazi, ndababwira yuko icyiza kuri bo ari uko bagumya kumera nkanjye. 
7:9 Ariko niba badashobora kwirinda barongorane, kuko ibyiza ari ukurongorana kuruta gushyuha.
7:10   </span><span class="note x"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body">    Mat 5.32; 19.9; Mar 10.11-12; Luka 16.18  
7:11 Ariko niba yahukanye, abe igishubaziko cyangwa yiyunge n'umugabo we, kandi umugabo ye gusenda umugore we.
7:12 Ariko abandi bo ni jye ubabwira si Umwami wacu. Mwene Data niba afite umugore utizera, kandi uwo mugore agakunda kugumana na we ye kumusenda. 
7:13 Kandi umugore ufite umugabo utizera na we agakunda kugumana na we, ye kwahukana n'umugabo we 
7:14 kuko umugabo utizera yezwa ku bw'umugore we, kandi umugore utizera yezwa ku bwa mwene Data uwo. Iyo bitameze bityo abana banyu baba bahumanye, ariko none dore ni abera. 
7:15 Icyakora wa wundi utizera, niba ashaka gutana atane. Mwene Data w'umugabo cyangwa w'umugore ntaba agihambiriwe iyo bimeze bityo, kuko Imana yaduhamagariye amahoro. 
7:16 Wa mugore we, ubwirwa n'iki yuko utazakiza umugabo wawe? Nawe wa mugabo we, ubwirwa n'iki yuko utazakiza umugore wawe?
7:17 Ariko umuntu wese agenze nk'uko Umwami wacu yabimugeneye, kandi amere uko yari ari Imana ikimuhamagara. Uko ni ko ntegeka mu matorero yose. 
7:18 Mbese hariho umuntu wahamagawe yarakebwe? Nuko rero ntagahinduke nk'utakebwe. Hariho umuntu wahamagawe atakebwe? Nuko ntagakebwe. 
7:19 Gukebwa nta cyo kumaze no kudakebwa na ko nta cyo kumaze, ahubwo ikigira icyo kimara ni ukwitondera amategeko y'Imana. 
7:20 Umuntu wese agume uko yari ari agihamagarwa. 
7:21 Mbese wahamagawe uri imbata? Ntibikubabaze. Icyakora niba ushobora kubātūrwa ubikore. 
7:22 Uwahamagawe n'Umwami wacu ari imbata aba abātūwe n'Umwami, kandi uwahamagawe n'Umwami ari uw'umudendezo aba ari imbata ya Kristo. 
7:23 Mwacungujwe igiciro, nuko rero ntimukabe imbata z'abantu. 
7:24 Bene Data, umuntu wese abane n'Imana ameze uko yari ameze agihamagarwa.
7:25 Ibyerekeye abari simfite itegeko ry'Umwami wacu, ariko ndababwira ibyo nibwira ndi umuntu wababariwe n'Umwami ngo nkiranuke.
7:26 Nuko ndibwira yuko ari byiza ku bw'iki gihe kirushya kiriho none, ko umuntu aguma uko ari. 
7:27 Mbese wahambiriwe ku mugore? Ntushake guhamburwa. Wahambuwe ku mugore? Nuko ntushake undi. 
7:28 Icyakora warongora nta cyaha waba ukoze. N'umwari yashyingirwa nta cyaha yaba akoze. Ariko abameze batyo bazagira imibabaro mu mubiri, ku bwanjye nakunda kuyibakiza.
7:29 Ariko bene Data, ibi ni ibyo mvuga yuko igihe kigabanutse. Uhereye none abafite abagore bamere nk'abatabafite, 
7:30 kandi abarira bamere nk'abatarira, n'abishīma bamere nk'abatishīma, n'abagura bamere nk'abatagira icyo bafite, 
