14:1 Mushimikire urukundo kandi mwifuze impano z'Umwuka, ariko cyane cyane mwifuze guhanura. 
14:2 Uvuga ururimi rutamenyekana si abantu abwira keretse Imana, kuko ari ntawumva ahubwo mu mwuka avuga amayoberane. 
14:3 Ariko uhanura we abwira abantu ibyo kubungura n'ibyo kubahugura, n'ibyo kubahumuriza. 
14:4 Uvuga ururimi rutamenyekana ariyungura, ariko uhanura yungura Itorero.
14:5 Nakunda ko mwese muvuga izindi ndimi, ariko ibirutaho ko muhanura. Uhanura aruta uvuga izindi ndimi, keretse azisobanuye kugira ngo Itorero ryunguke. 
14:6 Ariko none bene Data, ninza iwanyu mvuga indimi zitamenyekana nzabamarira iki, nintababwira ibyo mpishuriwe cyangwa ibyo mpawe kumenya, cyangwa guhanura cyangwa kwigisha?
14:7 Dore ibidafite ubugingo na byo bigira amajwi, ari umwironge cyangwa inanga, ariko iyo bidatandukanije amajwi yabyo, babwirwa n'iki ikivuzwa cyangwa igicurangwa icyo ari cyo? 
14:8 Kandi n'impanda na yo ivuze ijwi ritamenyekana, ni nde wakwitegura gutabara? 
14:9 Namwe ni uko, ururimi rwanyu nirutavuga ibimenyekana, bazabwirwa n'iki ibyo muvuga ibyo ari byo, ko muzaba mugosorera mu rucaca? 
14:10 Indimi zo mu isi nubwo ari nyinshi zite nta rudafite uko rusobanurwa. 
14:11 Nuko ntamenye uko ururimi rusobanurwa, nabera uvuga umunyamahanga kandi n'uvuga na we yambera umunyamahanga. 
14:12 Nuko rero namwe ubwo mushimikira kubona impano z'Umwuka, abe ari ko murushaho gushishikarira kuzūnguza Itorero.
14:13 Nuko uvuga ururimi rutamenyekana asabe, kugira ngo ahabwe no gusobanura. 
14:14 Iyo nsenga mu rurimi rutamenyekana umwuka wanjye urasenga, ariko ubwo bwenge bwanjye ntibugira icyo bwungura abandi. 
14:15 Nuko noneho ngire nte? Nzajya nsengesha umwuka wanjye ariko kandi nzajya nsengesha n'ubwenge, nzaririmbisha umwuka wanjye ariko kandi nzaririmbisha n'ubwenge. 
14:16 Utabikoze nawe ugashima Imana uyishimishije umwuka wawe wonyine, umuntu uri mu ruhande rw'injiji akaba atamenye icyo uvuze, yabasha ate kwikiriza ati “Amen”, umaze gushima? 
14:17 Ku bwawe uba ushimye neza koko, ariko wa wundi nta cyo aba yungutse.
14:18 Nshimira Imana yuko mwese mbarusha kuvuga indimi zitamenyekana, 
14:19 ariko mu iteraniro aho kuvuga amagambo inzovu mu rurimi rutamenyekana, nahitamo kuvuga amagambo atanu nyavugishije ubwenge bwanjye, kugira ngo nigishe n'abandi.
14:20 Bene Data, ntimube abana bato ku bwenge, ahubwo mube abana b'impinja ku bibi, ariko ku bwenge mube bakuru. 
